---
title: Adam Mish
layout: default
---

<div class=" text-center">
  <p>I write <a href="/poems">poetry</a>,
    <a href="/music">music</a>,
    <a href="/code">code</a>,
    <a href="https://twitter.com/adammish">tweets</a>,
    and <a href="/blog">blog posts</a>.
  </p>
  <p>I publish a poem every day,</p>
  <p>a blog post once a week,</p>
  <p>and blog posts whenever the mood strikes.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row px-4">
  <div class="latest-poem md:w-1/2 py-6">
    <p class="italic">Today's poem:</p>
      {%- for item in collections.poem | head(-1) -%}
        <p class="font-bold">{{ item.data.title }}</p>
        {{ item.templateContent | safe }}
      {%- endfor -%}
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="#">yesterday's poem</a> &bull; 
        <a href="/poems">all poems</a>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="latest-track md:w-1/2 py-6">
    <p class="italic">Latest track:</p>
      {%- for item in collections.track | head(-1) -%}
        <p class="font-bold">
          <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
        </p>
        {{ item.templateContent | section | safe }}
      {%- endfor -%}
    <div class="mt-8">
    <a href="/blog">all tracks</a> &bull; 
        <a href="/poems">spotify</a>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="px-4">
  <div class="latest-posts py-6">
    <p class="italic">Latest posts:</p>
      {%- for item in collections.post | head(-3) | reverse -%}
        <p class="font-bold">
          <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
        </p>
        {{ item.templateContent | section | safe }}
      {%- endfor -%}
    <p class="mt-8"><a href="/blog">all posts</a></p>
  </div>
</div>
